    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This 1988 Porsche 911 Carrera 3.2 represents the pinnacle of air-cooled refinement, featuring the coveted Getrag G50 five-speed transaxle with improved synchromesh for precise shift gates. The 3.2-liter horizontally opposed six-cylinder engine utilizes Bosch Motronic fuel injection, delivering linear power across the rev range with zero oil seepage. Its chassis remains taut, riding on original-spec longitudinal torsion bars and Bilstein dampers, while the four-piston calipers and ventilated rotors offer exceptional thermal management. Meticulously maintained with matching numbers and a flawless undercarriage, this example provides a visceral, analog driving experience in an unparalleled state of preservation.",
      "price": 49500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Mint condition. Low mileage. Original paint. Clean title. Garage kept. No mechanical issues. Interior is like new.",
