      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this absolute gem! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it honestly looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or ding in sight\u2014it\u2019s in truly pristine shape. It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept in a climate-controlled garage. I'm looking for a quick sale to a good home, so come take a look before someone else snags it!",
