      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 in a condition that defies its vintage. This specimen features the legendary S54 straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual. The double-VANOS system has been meticulously serviced, and the rear subframe\u2014a known point of fatigue\u2014has been professionally reinforced to ensure optimal chassis rigidity. Power is managed via the factory M-Variable differential lock, providing exceptional mechanical grip. The factory finish remains flawless, with no evidence of oxidation or clear-coat failure. Inside, the Nappa leather bolsters show zero compression or wear, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and preventative maintenance. This is a turn-key example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection and historical authenticity.",
